{"tid":1153321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以色列擬戈蘭高地建特朗普殖民區","createTime":"2019-05-13T14:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T14:06:20.000Z","uid":51620,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"010145977563e4b4d5c7577ce9a8db471c138ec7","tid":1153321,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T14:05:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=347746\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D347746&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHTwRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=e3e877d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D347746&h=7f646455\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=347746</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】以色列總理內塔尼亞胡表示，已在戈蘭高地選址興建以美國總統特朗普名字命名的殖民區。<br />\n<br />\n內塔尼亞胡主持內閣會議，再次讚揚特朗普承認耶路撒冷為以色列首都，並承認以色列在戈蘭高地主權，形容是歷史性的決定，他表示已在戈蘭高地選定地點興建以特朗普命名的殖民區。<br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒報道，選址位於戈蘭高地北部，最快下月舉行奠基儀式，首階段會有120個家庭遷入，以色列在1967年第三次中東戰爭中擊敗敘利亞並佔領戈蘭高地，但國際社會一直拒絕承認。"},{"pid":"71584d1f5eb2164b21bea50236db7086b362827d","tid":1153321,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T14:06:20.000Z","msg":"侵略暴行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}